<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">In unrelated news,<a class=3D"footnote-index" =
href=3D"#footnote-3" style=3D"color: #000000; text-decoration: none !import=
ant; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-=
style: none !important; background-color: transparent !important; display: =
inline-block;">
<span>[3]</span>
</a> I want to talk about two risky bets related to Sam Bankman-Fried=E2=80=
=99s criminal trial.</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">First, people <a href=3D"https://link.mail.blo=
ombergbusiness.com/click/32983479.262420/aHR0cHM6Ly9zbGF0ZS5jb20vdGVjaG5vbG=
9neS8yMDIzLzEwL3NiZi10cmlhbC1wcm9zZWN1dGlvbi1wbGVhLWRlYWwuaHRtbD9wYXk9MTY5N=
