<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">In November 2022, after=C2=A0FTX went bankrupt=
, Binance, the biggest crypto exchange, announced an =E2=80=9Cindustry reco=
very fund=E2=80=9D to do bailouts for crypto. Changpeng =E2=80=9CCZ=E2=80=
=9D Zhao, Binance=E2=80=99s founder, <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloomberg=
business.com/click/32983479.262420/aHR0cHM6Ly90d2l0dGVyLmNvbS9jel9iaW5hbmNl=
L3N0YXR1cy8xNTkyMDQ0NDk2MTc0NjEyNDgy/607f07ceef4b8524a319a23cBacf2ed9c" ite=
mprop=3D"StoryLink" itemscope=3D"itemscope" target=3D"_blank" style=3D"colo=
r: #000000; text-decoration: none !important; border-bottom-width: 1px; bor=
der-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: solid; background-color: #c=
cc;">tweeted</a> that the fund would =E2=80=9Chelp projects who are otherwi=
se strong, but in a liquidity crisis.=E2=80=9D As Bloomberg=E2=80=99s Emily=
 Nicolle <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/32983479.=
262420/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYmxvb21iZXJnLmNvbS9uZXdzL2FydGljbGVzLzIwMjMtMTAtMTAv=
YmluYW5jZS1zLTEtYmlsbGlvbi1wbGFuLXRvLXNhdmUtY3J5cHRvLWFmdGVyLWZ0eC1oYXMtcXV=
pZXRseS1maXp6bGVkLW91dD9jbXBpZD1CQkQxMDEwMjNfTU9ORVlTVFVGRiZ1dG1fbWVkaXVtPW=
VtYWlsJnV0bV9zb3VyY2U9bmV3c2xldHRlciZ1dG1fdGVybT0yMzEwMTAmdXRtX2NhbXBhaWduP=
