<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">We <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusin=
ess.com/click/32983479.262420/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYmxvb21iZXJnLmNvbS9vcGluaW9uL=
2FydGljbGVzLzIwMjMtMTAtMDkvb3plbXBpYy1pcy1iYWQtZm9yLWJ1c2luZXNzP2NtcGlkPUJC=
