yJnV0bV90ZXJtPTIzMTAxMCZ1dG1fY2FtcGFpZ249bW9uZXlzdHVmZg/607f07ceef4b8524a31=
9a23cCf2970e66" itemprop=3D"StoryLink" itemscope=3D"itemscope" target=3D"_b=
lank" style=3D"color: #000000; text-decoration: none !important; border-bot=
tom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: solid; b=
ackground-color: #ccc;">  talked yesterday</a> about a hypothetical drug, =
=E2=80=9Ca drug that reduces consumption in general, a universal demand sup=
pressant,=E2=80=9D which puts its users into such a Zen state of contentmen=
t that they have no need for other goods or services.=C2=A0This drug would =
have weird economic effects: A pharmaceutical company could perhaps make a =
lot of money selling it, but lots of=C2=A0<em>other=C2=A0</em>companies =E2=
=80=94=C2=A0the companies that sell consumption, that sell snacks and alcoh=
ol and airplane tickets and streaming video and internet ads =E2=80=94=C2=
=A0would lose money. And in our world of universal common ownership of the =
stock market, there would be a tension between a pharmaceutical company mak=
ing money from this drug and costing its owners money as all their=C2=A0<em=
>other=C2=A0</em>portfolio companies lose business.</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">This was of course inspired by Ozempic and Weg=
ovy and=C2=A0similar new appetite-suppressing drugs. But while they are=C2=
=A0<em>a little=C2=A0</em>like that hypothetical drug, they aren=E2=80=99t=
=C2=A0<em>really.=C2=A0</em>For one thing, these drugs=C2=A0don=E2=80=99t s=
uppress demand all that much, and to the extent they do it is mostly demand=
 for snacks and alcohol, not for vacations or social media posts. Realistic=
ally people on Ozempic will probably just spend less money on snacks and mo=
re money on cars or whatever.</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Meanwhile, Ozempic has some good-for-business =
effects. A bunch of readers pointed out that Ozempic might lengthen lifespa=
ns, which is good for consumption: You eat fewer snacks per year, but you h=
ave more years, so maybe you eat more snacks overall.=C2=A0</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">And you probably take just as many vacations, =
but you burn less jet fuel getting there. Bloomberg=E2=80=99s=C2=A0Mary Sch=
langenstein <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/329834=
79.262420/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYmxvb21iZXJnLmNvbS9uZXdzL2FydGljbGVzLzIwMjMtMDktM=
jkvd2VpZ2h0LWxvc3MtZHJ1Z3Mtb3plbXBpYy13ZWdvdnktY291bGQtcmVkdWNlLWFpcmxpbmVz=
LWNvc3RzP2NtcGlkPUJCRDEwMTAyM19NT05FWVNUVUZGJnV0bV9tZWRpdW09ZW1haWwmdXRtX3N=
vdXJjZT1uZXdzbGV0dGVyJnV0bV90ZXJtPTIzMTAxMCZ1dG1fY2FtcGFpZ249bW9uZXlzdHVmZg=
/607f07ceef4b8524a319a23cBaa19762b" itemprop=3D"StoryLink" itemscope=3D"ite=
mscope" target=3D"_blank" style=3D"color: #000000; text-decoration: none !i=
mportant; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; border-bo=
ttom-style: solid; background-color: #ccc;">  reported last month</a>:</p>
<blockquote>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Airlines and planemakers obsess about reducing=
 jet-fuel consumption by constantly finding new ways to reduce aircraft wei=
ght. They may have new allies in Ozempic and other similar slimming medicat=
ions.</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">United Airlines Holdings Inc. would save $80 m=
illion a year if the average passenger weight falls by 10 pounds, Sheila Ka=
hyaoglu, a Jefferies Financial analyst, estimated in a report Friday. Her w=
ork was part of a broader Jefferies analysis of public enthusiasm for the d=
rug and potential beneficiaries of its use. =E2=80=A6</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Other industries seen benefiting from the grow=
th of weight-loss drugs include pharmaceuticals, apparel =E2=80=94 particul=
arly athletic clothing =E2=80=94 and cosmetics, the Jefferies report said. =
A negative effect could hit restaurants and some food and beverage producer=
s if consumers shift to healthier eating or stop buying some products. The =
high cost of the drugs could lower spending for things like furniture or tr=
avel, it said.</p>
</blockquote>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">If everyone loses 30 pounds they will all have=
 to buy new clothes, which is good for the clothing business.</p>
